The eight-month-old little boy was last seen at his Scottsdale home on Tuesday. CAPE TOWN The circumstances surrounding the apparent kidnapping of an eight-month-old Kraaifontein baby are being investigated. The little boy was last seen at his Scottsdale home on Tuesday. Dessie Rechner of missing people s NGO, The Pink Ladies, says a woman is suspected of kidnapping the baby. The clothing worn by the baby was red and if you have any information please contact the police or The Pink Ladies. 